  <brief_title>Phase II Study of Pre-Operative Chemotherapy in Patients With Resectable Local-Regional Carcinoma of Esophagus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Pre-Operative Chemotherapy With Taxol, Cisplatin, and 5-Fluorouracil Followed by G-CSF in Patients With Resectable Local-Regional Carcinoma of Esophagus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
